the bitterness of being set up by someone despicable,

316
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:43,040
the pain
of watching your loved one die before you,

317
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:45,820
the darkness
of being sealed away for 500 years,

318
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:50,550
