of being betrayed by the one you loved?

319
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:53,890
I've never seen light in my life.

320
00:24:54,070 --> 00:24:56,670
So I'll drag you all down with me!

321
00:25:05,310 --> 00:25:07,120
Wangquan Hongye,

322
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:10,030
