331
00:25:45,510 --> 00:25:47,200
You sure

332
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:49,680
talk a lot today.

333
00:25:51,850 --> 00:25:53,360
You've lost everything

334
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:57,640
because you're narrow-minded, obsessed,

335
00:25:58,350 --> 00:26:00,680
and treat all living beings like insects.

336
00:26:15,540 --> 00:26:17,740
The love and light in this world…

337
00:26:18,790 --> 00:26:20,790
