338
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:27,120
Unparalleled Sword!

339
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:50,670
Jiuhuo.

340
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:52,480
Your demonic energy is depleted,

341
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:54,550
