349
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,810
There were moments of brilliance…

350
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,790
and also moments of darkness.

351
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:52,790
I admit my mistakes…

352
00:27:56,030 --> 00:27:57,750
but I have no regrets.

353
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:02,030
Wangquan Hongye,

354
00:28:03,310 --> 00:28:05,790
if your Unparalleled Sword can kill me,

355
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:09,680
