00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:34,000
are spineless cowards.

411
00:31:36,830 --> 00:31:37,750
Domineering?

412
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,290
Without Spiritual Blood,

413
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:43,030
